---
import BlockOffLayout from '../../layouts/BlockOffLayout.astro';
---

<BlockOffLayout
  title="Terms and Conditions | Block OFF"
  description="Read the Block OFF Terms and Conditions for using our AI comment moderation service."
  canonicalPath="/blockoff/terms"
>
  <header class="site-header page-header">
    <a class="brand" href="/blockoff" aria-label="Block OFF home"><img src="/blockoff/block-off-logo.png" alt="" /><span>Block OFF</span></a>
    <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="Primary navigation">
      <a href="/blockoff/#product">Product</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/#how">How it works</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/#dashboard">Dashboard</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/#pricing">Pricing</a>
    </nav>
    <a class="header-cta" href="/blockoff/#pricing">Try now</a>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <span class="section-kicker">Legal</span>
      <h1>Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p>Last updated: July 7, 2026. These terms explain the rules for using Block OFF and joining the early access launch.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="legal-layout">
      <nav class="legal-nav" aria-label="Terms sections">
        <a href="#service">Service</a>
        <a href="#accounts">Accounts</a>
        <a href="#moderation">Moderation</a>
        <a href="#payments">Payments</a>
        <a href="#limits">Limits</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <article class="legal-content">
        <section id="service"><h2>1. The service</h2><p>Block OFF is a planned AI comment moderation service for creators and teams. The product is intended to scan, classify, hide, review, restore, and report on comments from supported social platforms such as YouTube and Instagram.</p><p>Some features may be in early access, beta, private testing, or development. We may change, add, pause, or remove features as the product evolves.</p></section>
        <section id="accounts"><h2>2. Accounts and access</h2><p>You are responsible for the accounts you connect, the permissions you grant, and the moderation settings you choose. You must have the right to manage any social account you connect to Block OFF.</p><p>You agree not to use Block OFF to violate platform rules, impersonate others, access accounts without permission, or interfere with another user's community.</p></section>
        <section id="moderation"><h2>3. Moderation decisions</h2><p>AI moderation can make mistakes. A comment may be incorrectly hidden, allowed, or marked for review. Block OFF is designed to help you manage risk, but you remain responsible for your community standards and final moderation choices.</p><p>We recommend using review-first workflows during setup, especially before enabling automatic actions on high-volume accounts.</p></section>
        <section id="payments"><h2>4. Launch offer and payments</h2><p>The founding creator offer is currently positioned as three months of early access for the price of one month. Checkout is handled through Dodo Payments. Any paid plan, renewal, refund, or cancellation terms will be shown at checkout before you pay.</p></section>
        <section id="limits"><h2>5. Platform limits and availability</h2><p>Block OFF depends on third-party platforms, APIs, permissions, quotas, and review processes. YouTube, Instagram, Meta, Google, or other providers may change their rules or limit access.</p><p>We do not guarantee uninterrupted access to every platform feature. We will try to design around platform constraints while keeping the product compliant and reliable.</p></section>
        <section id="contact"><h2>6. Contact</h2><p>For questions about these terms, contact <a href="mailto:hello@blockoff.app">hello@blockoff.app</a>.</p></section>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer class="site-footer">
    <a class="brand footer-brand" href="/blockoff" aria-label="Block OFF home"><img src="/blockoff/block-off-logo.png" alt="" /><span>Block OFF</span></a>
    <nav aria-label="Footer navigation">
      <a href="/blockoff/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/terms">Terms & Conditions</a>`r`n      <a href="/blockoff/returns">Returns & Refunds</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/about">About Us</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/contact">Contact Us</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/support">Support</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/changelog">Changelog</a>
    </nav>
  </footer>
</BlockOffLayout>
